Featuring the words 'home is wherever I’m with you' in a hand drawn script surrounded by different homes such as lighthouse, mountains and a small cabin. 

The card is screen printed in white on brown kraft paper stock. 

The design is screen printed in my studio using high quality inks and 300 GSM brown kraft paper stock.

description:
